    "To handle non-recyclable and unfamiliar items gracefully by rejecting them, without requiring a dedicated training class for every possible object.",
    "To develop a secure, layered backend that manages user accounts, machines, recycling sessions, reward points, and reward redemptions, exposing its functionality through a documented web API.",
